Pseudo code 

User Story:
Change the color of the backgorund to reflect a user's mood

Action:
	1.Background is yellow
	2.Text is "sunshiny feeling"
	3.Click on button 
	    if background is yellow 
		text will change to (rainy day feeling)
		background color will change to blue
		else if backgorund is blue 
		back to original

	4.Background color will change 
	5.Click again 
	6.Background color appears 